{"tid":668924,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞銀料德國捧世界盃機會最大","createTime":"2018-05-18T04:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T09:15:41.000Z","uid":76855,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7dbc973b9213a105b647163eee81938523cf13de","tid":668924,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:44:01.000Z","msg":"距離2018年俄羅斯世界盃開鑼不足一個月，瑞銀(UBS)發表預測，稱德國捧盃機會最高。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c423592341f2a7a1078fec65f863c27458b43c4","tid":668924,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:44:20.000Z","msg":"瑞銀全球財富管理部門的投資總監辦公室，使用通常用於分析投資機會的計量經濟學工具進行預測。結果顯示，德國奪冠機會高達24%，緊隨其後的是巴西和西班牙，分別為19.8%和16.1%，往後依次是英格蘭、法國和比利時，分別有8.5%、7.3%和5.3%的機會。"},{"pid":"940dbb5fd2da588c1112a3bfc261173b8c7a3c82","tid":668924,"uid":48993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:45:08.000Z","msg":"收皮啦烏拉圭都冇"},{"pid":"1e3384604577fe96b43de4e90a469acc12f50df7","tid":668924,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:46:28.000Z","msg":"冇阿根庭已經唔洗睇"},{"pid":"d0e28bac52f0e622777210a2780c3b6e060ac4af","tid":668924,"uid":21190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:47:04.000Z","msg":"葡萄牙？亞軍庭？"},{"pid":"ce6d88d0ddb9f6d8430233b3cbc506e6142e2023","tid":668924,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"940dbb5fd2da588c1112a3bfc261173b8c7a3c82","tid":668924,"uid":48993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:45:08.000Z","msg":"收皮啦烏拉圭都冇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:47:16.000Z","msg":"烏拉圭 1.8%"},{"pid":"41efc0a508799fbaa6555f57d93f8649cf8db1a3","tid":668924,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e3384604577fe96b43de4e90a469acc12f50df7","tid":668924,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:46:28.000Z","msg":"冇阿根庭已經唔洗睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T04:47:29.0